description: Represents a romantic couple, specifically a woman with a light skin tone and a man with a medium skin tone, bound by love. Often used to express affection, romance, and partnership.
apple_vendor_description: This representation of a couple with a heart on Apple devices features a woman with a light skin tone and a man with a medium skin tone, their figures gently merging. A soft, glowing heart hovers between them, rendered with Apple’s signature smooth gradients and subtle 3D depth. The overall aesthetic is warm and affectionate, perfect for expressing love and strong bonds between two people on Apple devices.
